<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Group Invitation</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #1a1a1a;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f8fafc;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 40px auto;
            background: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 24px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px -5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), 0 8px 10px -6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6366f1 0%, #a855f7 100%);
            padding: 40px 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .logo {
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: #ffffff;
            letter-spacing: -0.025em;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 40px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        h1 {
            font-size: 24px;
            color: #1e293b;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            letter-spacing: -0.01em;
        }
        p {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #475569;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }
        .group-highlight {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            background: #f1f5f9;
            border-radius: 12px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #4f46e5;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 16px 32px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6366f1 0%, #a855f7 100%);
            color: #ffffff !important;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 700;
            border-radius: 14px;
            transition: transform 0.2s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.3);
        }
        .footer {
            padding: 24px;
            background-color: #f8fafc;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #94a3b8;
            border-top: 1px solid #f1f5f9;
        }
        .footer a {
            color: #6366f1;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
            .container {
                margin: 0;
                border-radius: 0;
            }
            .content {
                padding: 30px 20px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <a href="#" class="logo">Routiq</a>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <h1>Adventure awaits!</h1>
            <p>Hi there,</p>
            <p><strong><%= inviterName %></strong> has invited you to join their travel group:</p>
            <div class="group-highlight">
                <%= groupName %>
            </div>
            <p>Collaborate on itineraries, vote for activities, and plan the perfect trip together.</p>
            <a href="<%= inviteUrl %>" class="button">Accept Invitation</a>
            <p style="margin-top: 32px; font-size: 14px;">If the button doesn't work, copy and paste this link into your browser:<br>
            <span style="color: #6366f1;"><%= inviteUrl %></span></p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; 2026 Routiq Travel. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p>You received this email because you're a registered user on Routiq.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
